bloodawakensme
Hey there community, Well I wanna name some of my favorite bands that I hope you guys have heard of but if not they'll grow on you if you download them.

Ted leo and the pharmicists- Awesome band this guy Ted leo can spin politics or anything into his lyrics and they never cease to amaze me. Definetly worth a shot.

Stutterfly- Hmm not very Emo for you guys out there sorry. But this band can hardcore their brains out they're not that Hawthorne heights "type" Im following a plan band. No offense to the Hawthorne heights fans I like them too but they sound too processed to me. But very good at that sound.

Cursive- Whoa awesome band man they have some deep emo lyriced songs that I just can't get outta my head when Monday comes.

Well I hope you find something in these bands you like.
